Package it.unisannio.CARE.model.bloodBag

Class BloodBag

java.lang.Object
it.unisannio.CARE.model.bloodBag.BloodBag
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<BloodBag>
public class BloodBag
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<BloodBag>
The BloodBag class contains all the information about the registered blood bag, such as the serial number, creation date and expiration date and the donor code.
